<body class="text-center">

  <div class="mb-3 form-signing">
    <h1>Welcome to Remote Axe</h1>
    <h2>A website where you can download your files stored one computer from another.</h2>
    <h3>Please Register or Login and then follow the steps.</h3>
    <br />
    <h1>Register/Login</h1>
    <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder="Username" required>
